## ‚ú® Key Features (Both Apps)

- **üéµ High-Quality Streaming**: Listen to your favorite tracks in the best possible quality
- **üíæ Offline Downloads**: Save music directly to your device for offline listening
- **‚ù§Ô∏è Like & Collect**: Build your personal collection by liking songs
- **üîÑ Background Playback**: Continue listening while using other apps

- **üíæ Persistent State**: Your liked songs and recently played tracks are saved across app restarts
